Message.Jp: ザンドラ東部名産品の入手依頼

Message.En:
I'm a traveling merchant, and in eastern Zandra,
we can obtain good-quality 
<LQIM>. Due to high
demand from other regions, it's scarce. Deliver
about <LQVA> pieces, and I'll pay a fair price.
